Interface IDefinitionNode

    AccessorNode, BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode, BaseDefinitionNode, BaseTypedDefinitionNode, BaseVariableNode, ChainedVariableNode, ClassNode, ConfigConstNode, ConfigNamespaceNode, EffectTagNode, EventTagNode, FunctionNode, GetterNode, InterfaceNode, MemberedNode, MXMLClassDefinitionNode, MXMLDocumentNode, NamespaceNode, PackageNode, ParameterNode, SetterNode, StyleTagNode, VariableNode

    public interface IDefinitionNode
extends IASNode
    An AST node representing a declaration of a package, class, interface, function, parameter, variable, constant, or namespace.

    Each IDefinitionNode produces an IDefinition.
